Here you will find samples and guidance on how to build and extend your industry solution on the Dynamics 365 Business Application and Intelligence platforms using our industry accelerators. Samples will also include cross product implementations with Azure, Office 365, Power BI, LinkedIn, Teams and other on-premise and cloud based implementations.
